                    <tr><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">কার্বন টেট্রা-ক্লোরাইড</td><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">C</td><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">4</td><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Cl</td><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">1</td><td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"></td></tr>
