        </div>
        <h3 class="section-heading" style="text-align: center;">ভিটামিন K-র উৎস</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px;">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/100x100?text=ফুলকপি" alt="Cauliflower" style="border: 1px solid #ccc; margin: 5px;">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/100x100?text=দুধ" alt="Milk" style="border: 1px solid #ccc; margin: 5px;">
